      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Manager Brown of the Vancouver team filed protest\nwith President Lucas against the Spokane club protesting\n\n\nfive games played early in the and by the In\ndians The protest is made because Pitcher Holm and\nManager Ostdek helped the indians win those games be-\nfore being signed with the Spokane club.\n\n\nHolm pitched q game each against Tacoma and Van\ncouver, and Ostdek behind the bat in two against\nSeattle and against Vancouver Should the protest\nbe allowed these games will not count according to\nruling by the national commission Bob surely wants\nto reduce that big lead some way."
    }
  ]
